org.sql: SELECT members.* FROM members INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = members.project_id WHERE members.user_id = "$1" AND projects.status <> "$2" AND members.project_id = "$3" ORDER BY members.id ASC LIMIT "$4"

rewrites.sql: SELECT members.* FROM members WHERE members.user_id = "$1" AND members.project_id = "$3" ORDER BY members.id ASC LIMIT "$4"
